<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7617117>
    dc:description "Figs 10A–D. A, B – habitus images of living adults (photographs taken indoors) of Perissonemia occasa Drake, 1942 from Hyogo, Honshu, Japan:A – male, B – female. C – host plant (Osmanthus heterophyllus) for P. occasa at Hyogo, Honshu, Japan. D, E – habitus images of living adults (photographs taken indoors) of P. yaeyamensis sp. nov. from Ishigaki Island, Ryukyu Islands, Japan (D – male, E – female). F – host plant (O. marginatus) for P. yaeyamensis sp. nov. at Ishigaki Island, Ryukyu Islands, Japan." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7617117/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7617119>
    dc:description "Fig. 11. Collection sites of three species of Perissonemia from Japan used in present study. Red circles = P. occasa Drake, 1942; green squares = P. okinawensis sp. nov.; blue triangles = P. yaeyamensis sp. nov." ;
